spec_data.Name: perl-GD-SVG
spec_data.Description:
GD::SVG seamlessly enables the scalable vector graphics (SVG) output
from scripts written using GD.  It accomplishes this by translating GD
functions into SVG functions.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:45:25 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: GD::SVG enables SVG output from scripts written using GD
